      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a rewarding project! This car is in poor condition and needs some serious mechanical and cosmetic attention, making it the perfect choice for a talented mechanic or someone looking for a budget-friendly parts vehicle. It's a great opportunity to roll up your sleeves and breathe new life into a car with plenty of potential!",
