      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and cosmetic restoration to be roadworthy again. The engine is currently running roughly, and there are noticeable fluid leaks and suspension issues that need immediate repair. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several dents and areas of rust, while the interior requires a complete overhaul due to extensive wear and tear. This is strictly a project car or a source for parts, and it is recommended that any potential buyer brings a trailer for transport.",
