      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, entirely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather bolsters remain firm and matte, devoid of any creasing or wear, and the interior still carries that distinct factory fragrance. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the smallest ambient light, functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting its gentle history and preventative maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44500.0,
